headline: Bio-Techne, USP Partner to Enhance Monoclonal Antibody, Gene Therapy Development
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ:TECH) is one of the best S&P 500 stocks with huge upside potential. On June 24, Bio-Techne Corporation announced a distribution agreement with the US Pharmacopeia/USP. The collaboration allows Bio-Techne to sell USP monoclonal antibody/mAb and recombinant adeno-associated virus/AAV reference standards alongside its analytical solutions, like the Maurice system, to support the global […]
